id: pm-cpja
title: "GH-444: ergonomic author attribution — global --author, init author_default, unknown-author advisory"
description: "Dogfood GH-444: stateless CLI agents lose PM_AUTHOR between shell calls and mutations degrade to author 'unknown', breaking provenance. Duplicate check: searched author attribution/unknown fallback — only closed dedup refactor pm-xh0y; no open overlap."
